OL,3,CTravellers to face disruption as
OL,4,CSevern bridge and tunnel to shut
OL,6,FTravellers on the busiest routes
OL,7,Fbetween south Wales and England will
OL,8,Fface disruption in July as both the M4
OL,9,FSevern Bridge and Severn rail tunnel
OL,10,Fwill close for repairs between
OL,11,FWednesday 3 July and Friday 19 July.
OL,13,FGreat Western Railway (GWR) has
OL,14,Fannounced that due to "track renewal
OL,15,Fand essential drainage work" there
OL,16,Fwill be no direct trains running
OL,17,Fbetween south Wales and Bristol for
OL,18,Fseveral days next month.
