OL,6,FOn Saturday 20 July - the M4's
OL,7,Fwestbound carriageway will be shut
OL,8,Ffrom 9pm . Then on Sunday 21 July from
OL,9,F5am there will be a two-lane
OL,10,Fcontraflow in each direction and a
OL,11,Freduced speed limit on the bridge
OL,12,Fthrough the summer.
OL,14,FA GWR spokesperson announced: "Track
OL,15,Frenewal and essential drainage work
OL,16,Fwill affect all train services via the
OL,17,FSevern Tunnel with no direct trains
OL,18,Fbetween Bristol and South Wales.
