OL,4,CSevern bridge and tunnel to shut
OL,6,F"Trains between London and South Wales
OL,7,Fwill be diverted via Gloucester and as
OL,8,Fa result these services won't stop at
OL,9,FBristol Parkway. A limited number of
OL,10,Ftrains will be running between Bristol
OL,11,FParkway and London Paddington in the
OL,12,Fmorning and the evening only.
OL,14,F"Trains will run between Bristol
OL,15,FParkway and Portsmouth Harbour via
OL,16,FBristol Temple Meads, plus between
OL,17,FBristol Temple Meads and Taunton,
OL,18,FPlymouth or Penzance.
